WEBVTT

00:05.711 --> 00:10.533
Over the weekend, we saw an incredible response around the globe...

00:10.943 --> 00:14.225
...to Windows 8 and the Microsoft Surface.

00:14.908 --> 00:21.099
We're seeing preliminary demand well above where we were with Windows 7, which is gratifying.

00:21.647 --> 00:24.023
We're seeing retailers here in the United States...

00:24.105 --> 00:27.730
...and hardware manufacturers enthusiastic about the response.

00:28.260 --> 00:36.091
The demand for touch on all-in-ones and laptops in addition to tablets has been really quite astounding,...

00:36.545 --> 00:41.248
...and certainly the lines we've seen at the Microsoft stores have been heartening.

